ISLAMABAD, Jul 09 (APP):Speaker National Assembly Sardar Ayaz Sadiq on Tuesday announced six-member panel of chairpersons to conduct the business of 7th session of the House in the absence of Speaker and Deputy Speaker National Assembly.
The panel consists of Zahid Iqbal, Abdul Qadir Patel, Romina Khurshid Alam, Amin ul Haq, Shahida Begum and Riaz Fatyana who would chair the house proceedings in absence of the Speaker and Deputy Speaker National Assembly during the 7th session.
